<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/871434-i-m-curious-what-others-make-of-the">I&#39;m curious what others make of the chapter near the end in which Tarwater, after leaving the truck driver, gets in to the car with a stranger who turns out to be some sort of vampire-like pedophile. It seems that the implication is that this is his &quot;friend&quot; who&#39;s been driving him away from his great uncle&#39;s attempts at making him a prophet, but I&#39;m still not exactly sure what to make of it. Ideas?</a>
</div>
