<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I think the stranger is a symbol of evil, but also something else. Didn&apos;t the great-uncle warn Tarwater against riding with strangers? So the great-un<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I think the stranger is a symbol of evil, but also something else. Didn't the great-uncle warn Tarwater against riding with strangers? So the great-uncle was right once. Could he then be right in other ways, too?<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
