<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/803770-i-can-t-find-a-list-of-all-the-old">I can&#39;t find a list of all the Old Testament prophets listed in this book. The Old Man talks about Elijah and Elisha quite a bit (Kings). Azahiah gets mentioned (Chronicles). Who knows more?

I think reading about the lives of some Old Testament prophets would clear up a lot of confusion about the &#39;unpleasant&#39; personalities in this book.</a>
</div>
